-- Santander Said to Hire Banks for Mortgage-Backed Bond Issue
-- B y   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 2012-01-09T09:10:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-09/santander-said-to-hire-banks-for-mortgage-backed-bond-issue.html
Santander U.K. Plc hired banks to
manage a sale of mortgage-backed securities by Holmes Master
Issuer Plc Series 2012-1, according to three investors with
knowledge of the matter.  Banco Santander SA (SAN)  will manage the issue itself, along with
 Barclays Capital , Deutsche Bank and JPMorgan, said the
investors. It will sell the bonds when market conditions allow,
they said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Esteban Duarte in Madrid at 
